<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5020898>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 8. Consensus tree of the families of Patellidae and Nacellidae with the position of S. mexicana using maximum likelihood and Bayesian methods based on the mitochondrial COI mtDNA gene. The bootstrap values/posterior probabilities (ML/BI) are indicated under the principal nodes. The taxon names are followed by their GenBank accession numbers (S. mexicana specimens were sequenced in the present study). The shaded area indicates the position of S. mexicana." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/5020898/files/figure.png" .

